data.description: This unique ranch property sits on almost 1 acre of land located in Valley Acres. Home features nearly 1800 sq ft of living space with a open split wing floor plan. Upon Entry this home opens up to a oversized family living area, formal dining room, open large kitchen plan with a island as well as a second dining area for your family. Home features 3 bedrooms and 3 baths. The large main room has 2 complete separate bathrooms with a huge walk in closet that has entries on either side of the bathrooms. Once you walk through the indoor laundry room to the back yard you will see it has a mature fruit tree, as well as 2 large shade trees and a park like atmosphere with green grass. This area has a wash rack for your animals, horse pens and a large work shop and barn that has 3 horse stalls, 2 box stalls, a tack room and a bird aviary. Bring you animals and pets this property has plenty of room and access to many horse trails.
